# Cloudflare Pages headers — Veris members-only embed gate (Phase 2)
# Sits dormant on GitHub Pages (which ignores _headers).
# Activates when this repo is deployed via Cloudflare Pages.
# Browser refuses to render the page unless embedded inside a Circle domain.
# Tighten the wildcards to the exact Veris Circle subdomain once known.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors https://*.circle.so https://*.circle.com
